data.description: Well maintained home in a secluded subdivision! This property features 3 beds/ 2 baths, solar panels, tall ceilings, and abundant natural light.  Inside, an open floor plan living room and kitchen provide an inviting atmosphere.  The eat-in kitchen has stainless appliances, a bar, tile backsplash, dining area, and pantry closet.  The primary bedroom suite offers an attached bathroom with dual sink vanity, jetted tub, walk-in tiled shower, and walk-in closet.  Bedrooms 2 and 3 share a full hall bathroom.  The backyard has a large wooden deck and has a portion enclosed with a picket wood fence. Webb City Schools.
